FiKeyAuth - Class in com.github.dkanellis.fikey
The main class of the API which implements all the appropriate functionality in order for the U2F registration and login to be as simple as possible.
FiKeyAuth(String) - Constructor for class com.github.dkanellis.fikey.FiKeyAuth
 
finishDeviceAuthentication(String, String) - Method in interface com.github.dkanellis.fikey.Authenticator
 
finishDeviceAuthentication(String, String) - Method in class com.github.dkanellis.fikey.FiKeyAuth
Finishes the authentication of a device with a user by acquiring the user from the storage, then the response of the device, then matching the response against the request from our storage and then updating the device in the storage.
finishDeviceRegistration(String, String) - Method in interface com.github.dkanellis.fikey.Authenticator
 
finishDeviceRegistration(String, String) - Method in class com.github.dkanellis.fikey.FiKeyAuth
Finishes the registration of a device with a user by first acquiring the user from the storage, then the response of the device, then matching the response against the request from our storage and then adding the device to the user.
